description: Cibus Nordic Real Estate AB engages in the acquisition, development, and administration of properties for grocery and store chains. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 6 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2018-03-09. The company owns a portfolio consisting of more than 100 properties with lettable area of approximately 437,860 square meters. The portfolio is concentrated primarily in Sweden, Finland, Denmark and Norway. The Company’s main focus lies on the Helsinki region and the southern part of Finland with tenants mainly being Kesko, Tokmanni and S-Group.
name: Cibus Nordic Real Estate AB (publ)
